PrecisOrder (a) authorizing entry into several AGREEMENTS with CHARLOTTETOWN AIRPORT AUTHORITY INC. to effect the transfer of responsibility for the management, operation and maintenance of Charlottetown Airport, located in Queens County, Prince Edward Island, (b) designating the Authority as a "designated airport authority", and (c) specifying the date upon which the transfer will take effect.

precis:
Order (a) authorizing entry into several AGREEMENTS with CHARLOTTETOWN
AIRPORT AUTHORITY INC. to effect the transfer of responsibility for the
management, operation and maintenance of Charlottetown Airport, located
in Queens County, Prince Edward Island, (b) designating the Authority as a
"designated airport authority", and (c) specifying the date upon which the
transfer will take effect.
